properties.Name: Identification

Columns.Name: IdentificationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the identification.

Columns.Name: IdentificationValue
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the associated Identification from the perspective of the Issuing Party.

Columns.Name: IdentificationTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Identification Type.

Columns.Name: IdentificationFormId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Identification Form.

Columns.Name: IssuingPartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: CountryId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Country.

Columns.Name: IdentificationIssuedTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp the identification was issued.

Columns.Name: IdentificationExpiryTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp the identification is effective until.

Columns.Name: IdentificationCreationTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp the identification was created.

Columns.Name: IdentificationDestroyedTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp the identification was destroyed.

Columns.Name: IdentificationNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the identification.

Properties.Description:
Identification is used to identify individuals as well as equipment. 

Identification can be composed of one or more components. Identification can include a combination of photograph, barcode, magnetic strip, RFID, IR.

Some forms of identification such as a token or device may be worn for tracking purposes.
